The '''Thruncan Insurrection''', also known as the '''Thruncon Insurrection''', was a rebellion that took place prior to [[12 BBY/Legends|12 BBY]].<ref name="AIR">According to the [[1995]] sourcebook ''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]'', [[Xenon Nnaksta]] graduated from the [[Galactic Outdoor Survival School/Legends|Galactic Outdoor Survival School]] in around [[12 BBY/Legends|12 BBY]].</ref> Instigated by [[Vodran (species)/Legends|Vodrans]] living in the city of [[Thruncan]], on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Vodran/Legends|Vodran]] against the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] presence there, the results of the insurrection were unclear.

[[Xenon Nnaksta]]'s parents were killed during the attempted ousting.

